### 5.4 Configurar o `shopify.extension.toml`

Verifique que o arquivo `extensions/diboa-cashback-widget/shopify.extension.toml` contém:

```toml
api_version = "2025-01"

[[extensions]]
type = "theme"
name = "Diboa Cashback Widget"

  [extensions.capabilities]
